  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    Welcome to BulkMails. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you use our application.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>When you sign in using your Google account, we may collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your Google account email address</li>
    <li>Basic profile information provided by Google</li>
    <li>Access tokens required to authenticate your account</li>
    <li>Information necessary to send emails on your behalf</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information solely to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Authenticate your identity</li>
    <li>Allow you to access the application</li>
    <li>Send emails on your behalf when you explicitly request it</li>
    <li>Improve and maintain our services</li>
    <li>Provide customer support</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Google User Data</h2>
  <p>
    Our application uses Google OAuth to access authorized Google account information.
  </p>
  <p>
    We do not sell, rent, or share Google user data with third parties for advertising or marketing purposes.
  </p>
  <p>
    Any access to Google user data is limited to the functionality required for the operation of the application.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
  <p>
    We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
  </p>
  <p>
    Access tokens and user information are handled securely and used only for providing application functionality.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or trade your personal information.</p>
  <p>We may disclose information only when:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Required by law</li>
    <li>Necessary to protect our legal rights</li>
    <li>Required to provide the services requested by the user</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We retain user information only for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations.
  </p>
  <p>
    Users may request deletion of their data at any time.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Revoke Google account access at any time through your Google Account settings</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Contact us regarding privacy concerns</li>
